videos.description: Klay Thompson walks with the help of crutches and his left knee wrapped up after leaving Game 6 due to injury.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA News (Thompson leaves arena on crutches) 2019/06/13

videos.headline: Thompson leaves arena on crutches

videos.description: Tim Legler says the Raptors "thoroughly outplayed" the Warriors and says Kawhi Leonard's free throws is the cherry on top to the Raptors' title.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Legler: Kawhi icing the game was ‘very fitting’) 2019/6/13 SC

videos.headline: Legler: Kawhi icing the game was 'very fitting'

videos.description: Kyle Lowry talks about how he overcame adversity and touches upon his relationship with former teammate DeMar DeRozan, saying he loves him and will FaceTime him later.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Lowry: 'Canada, we brought it home!') 2019/6/13

videos.headline: Lowry: 'Canada, we brought it home!'

videos.description: Raptors President of Basketball Operations Masai Ujiri describes what winning a NBA championship means and sends words of thanks to the Warriors.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Ujiri: Raptors looked to prove something to the world) 2019/06/13

videos.headline: Ujiri: Raptors looked to prove something to the world

videos.description: Jalen Rose, Chauncey Billups and Paul Pierce break down the impact of Kawhi Leonard and the Raptors winning the NBA championship for the rest of the league.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Pierce: Kawhi’s run greatest run I have ever seen) 2019/06/13 ESHEET NBACD

videos.headline: Pierce: Kawhi's run greatest run I have ever seen

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith explains why he thought the Warriors were done when Klay Thompson left with injury in the third quarter of Game 6.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Stephen A.: ‘The outcome was inevitable’ when Klay left) 2019/06/13 ESHEET SVPSC

videos.headline: Stephen A.: 'The outcome was inevitable' when Klay left

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith agrees with SVP that even if Kawhi Leonard leaves via free agency, trading for him to win the NBA title was worth it.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Stephen A.: Kawhi trade worth the risk no matter what happens) 2019/06/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stephen A.: Kawhi trade worth the risk no matter what happens

videos.description: During the season, Nick Nurse stayed awake to watch Warriors games more than any other team, figuring if the Raptors made it to the Finals, they'd meet up.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Nick Nurse stayed up late to watch Warriors games) 2019/06/13

videos.headline: Nick Nurse stayed up late to watch Warriors games

videos.description: After finishing up his news conference, Kawhi Leonard gets up to leave and forgets his NBA Finals MVP trophy on the table.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Kawhi leaves behind Finals MVP trophy) 2019/06/13

videos.headline: Kawhi leaves behind Finals MVP trophy

videos.description: Kawhi Leonard says his goal in joining the Raptors was to bring the team to the NBA Finals and is proud of what he and his team accomplished. He also touched upon free agency.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Kawhi reaches his goal of ‘making history’) 2019/6/13 SVP SC

videos.headline: Kawhi reaches his goal of 'making history'

videos.description: Kawhi Leonard reveals that after he got traded to the Raptors, he texted Kyle Lowry saying, "let's go out and do something special."

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Leonard texted Lowry after trade to Toronto) 2019/06/13

videos.headline: Leonard texted Lowry after trade to Toronto

videos.description: Kyle Lowry tells SVP what it means to be a champion and what he plans to tell Kawhi Leonard ahead of NBA free agency.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Lowry explains what it means to be a world champion) 2019/06/13 ESHEET SVPSC

videos.headline: Lowry explains what it means to be a world champion

videos.description: Scott Van Pelt reflects in awe at Kawhi Leonard's career, as the 2019 NBA Finals MVP joins Kareem and LeBron as the only 3 players to earn the honor for 2 different teams.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Kawhi earns ‘top shelf’ respect at just 27 - SVP) 2019/6/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kawhi earns 'top shelf' respect at just 27 - SVP

videos.description: Kyle Lowry crashes Fred VanVleet's news conference and asks him what it is like to be an NBA champion.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Lowry crashes VanVleet’s news conference) 2019/06/13

videos.headline: Lowry crashes VanVleet's news conference

videos.description: After leading the Raptors to an NBA championship, Kawhi Leonard gets doused in champagne in the locker room.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA News (Kawhi gets champagne bath following title win) 2019/06/13

videos.headline: Kawhi gets champagne bath following title win

videos.description: Kawhi Leonard and Kyle Lowry tell Rachel Nichols how rough the season was at times but stop short of giving details.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Raptors’ rollercoaster season ends on the highest note) 2019/06/13

videos.headline: Raptors' roller-coaster season ends on the highest note

videos.description: Jay Williams calls Kawhi Leonard "the code breaker" of dismantling dynasties and says his second Finals MVP paves the way to Springfield.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Williams: Kawhi punched his ticket to HOF with 2nd Finals MVP) 2019/6/14 ESHEET GetUp

videos.headline: Williams: Kawhi punched his ticket to HOF with 2nd Finals MVP

videos.description: With the uncertain future of Kevin Durant and Klay Thompson's ACL tear, Jay Williams feels the Warriors' dynasty has come to an end.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Williams: Warriors' dynasty is done, but that's okay) 2019/6/14 ESHEET GetUp

videos.headline: Williams: Warriors' dynasty is done, but that's okay
